data.description: Newly updated 3-BD, 2.5-BA residence nestled in the Silver Pointe neighborhood. Conveniently near shopping & dining this home boasts an amazing open layout, ideal for modern living. The kitchen is equipped with SS appliances, abundant counter space, a walk-in pantry, & a separate utility closet. Flowing seamlessly into the dining area, it offers access to the fenced backyard, which backs onto a serene green belt for privacy. Enjoy evenings by the fireplace, enhanced by updated lighting & flooring throughout. Flexible bonus rooms on both levels provide versatile spaces. Upstairs, the primary suite boasts a generous size with a dedicated laundry & spacious private bath leading to a walk-in closet. Book a showing to view this exceptional home!
